1
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,480
My Lord, bad news.

2
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,520
What is it?

3
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,320
Someone has requested a night trial for the three suspects.

4
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,600
Who?

5
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:58,320
It is I.

6
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,960
I am Lu Shijie, the top lawyer of Shuntian Prefecture.

7
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:05,200
Commissioned by the Tang Clan.

8
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,520
Here are the appeal documents.

9
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,160
According to the Great Ming Code of Interrogation and Judgment...

10
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,440
Section 28, Article 29...

11
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,120
And Article 16.

12
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,240
I am filing a complaint against the Grand Court of Justice.

13
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,920
For, in the absence of sufficient evidence...

14
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,440
Arresting innocent civilians.

15
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,800
Namely Tang Xi, Yuan Ran, and Wu Qiangu.

16
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,400
Thank you, Lawyer Lu.

17
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,640
For saving us from this misery.

18
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,320
My old bones...

19
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,600
Can handle a little grievance, it doesn't matter.

20
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,640
But my poor sister Yuan Ran...

21
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,200
She has always been frail.

22
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,240
She was perfectly fine...

23
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,840
But the shock has triggered her hysteria.

24
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:39,960
And the crazy girl...

25
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,040
Was injured by the Vice Minister of the Dali Temple.

26
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,360
Her internal injuries haven't healed...

27
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,520
And now she's been frightened again.

28
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,840
Now...

29
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,160
She is suffering here!

30
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:50,360
Public morals are declining day by day!

31
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,800
Morality is in ruin!

32
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,920
The dignified Grand Court of Justice...

33
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:55,080
Would actually treat the old, weak, women, and children this way!

34
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,080
Lord Pei.

35
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,640
According to the Great Ming Code of Interrogation and Judgment...

36
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,040
Section 28, Article 29...

37
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,440
Article 4, Article 10, and Article 15.

38
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,920
I want to add a charge against the Grand Court for torturing the old and young.

39
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,840
For mental abuse.

40
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,280
Attempting to use severe torture and cruel laws...

41
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,600
To force a confession.

42
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,040
According to the laws of the Great Ming...

43
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,880
Your additional accountability...

44
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,200
Is not inappropriate.

45
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:15,440
However, this case...

46
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:19,840
Involves the Eastern Depot and the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

47
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:21,920
This...

48
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,720
Lawyer Lu.

49
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,040
These three people...

50
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,520
Although arrested by the Grand Court of Justice...

51
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,640
Were arrested at the request of the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

52
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:35,240
Let alone arrest, interrogation, or private torture...

53
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,760
Even if we were to execute them on the spot...

54
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,280
It falls within the scope of our authority.

55
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,800
This additional accountability...

56
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,640
Is invalid.

57
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,360
I was presumptuous.

58
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,720
Commander Shen has the authority of the Imperial Prison.

59
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,920
But judgment must follow a trial.

60
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,000
You would never place yourself above Imperial power...

61
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,160
And use unjust, false, and wrong cases...

62
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,840
To repay His Majesty's trust.

63
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:57,640
After all...

64
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,000
Since the founding of our dynasty...

65
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:01,120
We have governed the realm by law.

66
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,320
That...

67
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,560
Is naturally so.

68
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,760
To prevent others from speculating on the actions of the Depots and Guards...

69
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,880
And to show our innocence...

70
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,720
The murder case of the Superintendent...

71
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,640
Was handed over to the Grand Court of Justice.

72
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:13,680
We...

73
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,040
Are merely assisting.

74
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,960
The Grand Court of Justice, in accordance with the Great Ming Code,

75
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,800
shall enforce the law impartially,

76
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,400
without any negligence.

77
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,440
Now,

78
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:30,120
regarding the issues raised by Lawyer Lu Shijie,

79
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,400
we shall proceed with the inquiry.

80
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:33,160
Suspect Tang Xi.

81
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,400
Do you all know

82
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:37,080
why you were arrested and brought to the Grand Court of Justice today?

83
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,520
In reply, My Lord,

84
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,000
this commoner does not know.

85
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:42,800
Now, I invite Vice Minister Zhang Yi

86
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,800
to question the suspects.

87
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,560
Yes, My Lord.

88
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,120
Suspect Wu Qiangu,

89
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,680
suspected of using hallucinogenic potions

90
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,320
to disrupt order at the execution ground,

91
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,760
causing a commotion among the people,

92
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,680
and leading to the murder of the Commander.

93
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,640
Suspect Yuan Ran,

94
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,960
suspected of using puppets

95
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,920
to physically attack the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

96
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,040
Suspect Tang Xi,

97
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,440
suspected of disguising as the Snow Maiden Dou E,

98
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:08,160
assisting the criminal Li Chenyang in escaping the execution ground.

99
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,440
The three of you publicly mocked last night's robbery,

100
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:13,400
openly provoking the authority of the Grand Court of Justice and the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

101
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:14,600
Wu Qiangu,

102
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,800
Yuan Ran,

103
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:16,760
Tang Xi,

104
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:20,080
do you three admit to the crimes alleged by Vice Minister Zhang?

105
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,840
He's lying through his teeth.

106
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,320
This is a frame-up.

107
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,320
I am just a humble woman.

108
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,160
My Lord, please do not wrong an innocent person.

109
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:31,080
This commoner believes the Great Ming Code

110
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:33,480
will grant this commoner a fair and just verdict,

111
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,200
to restore my innocence.

112
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:37,160
The three refuse to plead guilty.

113
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:38,520
Now,

114
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,680
Lawyer, please defend the three.

115
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,200
Thank you, Lord Pei.

116
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,240
Our dynasty relies on evidence as the basis,

117
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,720
and the Great Ming Code as the criterion.

118
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,480
I dare to ask,

119
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,280
Vice Minister of the Dali Temple, Lord Zhang Yi,

120
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:50,920
you suspect Wu Qiangu of using illusion potions

121
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,800
to disrupt the execution ground order.

122
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:55,040
Is there any evidence to prove this?

123
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:55,880
Danqing.

124
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,280
Present the evidence.

125
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,600
This is what I collected:

126
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,480
willow catkins from the execution ground last night,

127
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,800
and the plum branches

128
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,480
that Wu Qiangu gifted to the people.

129
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,120
The agents in these two items,

130
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,800
when mixed together,

131
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,560
cause intense hallucinations

132
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,440
and lead one to attack and harm others.

133
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,720
The evidence provided by Lord Zhang seems sound.

134
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,240
I also witnessed the events yesterday.

135
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,840
Hearing the Lords explain it today,

136
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,320
it suddenly makes sense.

137
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,360
Wu Qiangu,

138
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,280
these plum blossoms,

139
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:23,080
are they what you gifted to the people?

140
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:23,840
In reply, My Lord,

141
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:24,920
these plum blossoms

142
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,000
are indeed mine.

143
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,680
But the potion within them

144
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,320
is to stimulate the blooming of the plum blossoms,

145
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,360
and is harmless.

146
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,520
It allows those who smell the plum blossoms

147
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,960
to feel refreshed and happy.

148
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:36,520
Then are these willow catkins from your home?

149
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:39,280
My home has no willow trees, so where would catkins come from?

150
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,720
If you insist on forcing this on me...

151
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,240
Willow catkins fly all over the capital.

152
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,040
Then are all the people of the capital

153
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,640
the owners of the willow catkins?

154
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,640
Everyone has heard.

155
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,720
Wu Qiangu admits to gifting plum blossoms to the people,

156
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,360
but does not admit to the matter of the willow catkins.

157
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,280
Just because of a harmless potion in the plum blossoms,

158
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:55,520
to frame Wu Qiangu, an alchemist,

159
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,160
is perhaps

160
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,720
a bit too rash, isn't it?

161
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:58,720
But within these willow catkins,

162
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,480
there is indeed a potion brewed by Wu Qiangu.

163
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,160
Lord Zhang,

164
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:03,040
has the Grand Court of Justice found

165
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:03,080
the potion formula handwritten by Wu Qiangu?

166
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:05,480
The potion formula handwritten by Wu Qiangu?

167
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,360
Or did this formula come from a witness?

168
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,120
Or perhaps

169
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:10,120
receipts for purchasing the potion ingredients?

170
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,720
There is currently no valid evidence.

171
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:16,560
Then,

172
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,560
you cannot convict based on this.

173
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,760
Without evidence or proof,

174
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,320
it is a frame-up, a false accusation.

175
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,840
It is Vice Minister Zhang's investigation

176
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,320
that is not thorough enough.

177
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,280
Lord Pei,

178
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,520
Commander Shen,

179
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,160
the Grand Court of Justice must not wrong

180
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,760
such a wandering performer,

181
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:34,360
and chill the hearts of all the people in the capital.

182
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,480
I only ask, my lords,

183
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:44,120
for fairness and justice, nothing more.

184
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,120
The number one lawyer of Shuntian Prefecture

185
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,960
lives up to his reputation.

186
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,160
Lawyer Lu,

187
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,520
I will make my own judgment.

188
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,960
Continue your questioning,

189
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,200
Vice Minister Zhang.

190
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,040
As for the evidence of Yuan Ran's crimes,

191
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,000
please ask the Grand Court of Justice coroner

192
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,560
to come forward and state the facts.

193
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:06,600
Reporting, my lord.

194
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:09,800
From the bodies of the deceased Embroidered Uniform Guards,

195
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:12,400
the fatal wounds were caused by falling into an illusion

196
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:15,000
and hacking each other with Embroidered Spring Swords.

197
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,040
However, the sword wounds on the bodies

198
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:20,160
differ from those made by the Embroidered Spring Swords.

199
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:20,600
Therefore,

200
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,360
I deduce that

201
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,880
it was Yuan Ran utilizing

202
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,600
puppets dressed as evil spirits

203
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,840
to mix in with the Guards and confuse them,

204
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,400
making the Embroidered Uniform Guards doubt

205
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,840
the reality of what they were seeing.

206
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,640
In this world,

207
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,400
how could anyone control

208
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:36,240
a puppet the same size as a human

209
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,640
and use it to harm people?

210
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,920
Among the many commoner witnesses present last night,

211
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,800
who

212
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,480
can prove that it was Yuan Ran controlling

213
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,560
these so-called puppets

214
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,680
to harm people?

215
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,560
Or perhaps,

216
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,280
if the puppets that caused harm were found,

217
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,440
let this humble one

218
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:49,440
take a look.

219
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:51,040
Last night, the people were all under an illusion.

220
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:53,080
In the chaos, everyone was only concerned with escaping.

221
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:53,720
No one saw

222
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,120
how she manipulated the puppets.

223
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,520
As for where the puppets are now,

224
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:58,200
that is a question for the criminal Yuan Ran.

225
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:00,760
My puppets are just wooden dolls for opera.

226
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,320
How could they possibly harm anyone?

227
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:04,760
My lord,

228
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:06,600
you overestimate me.

229
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,360
So,

230
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,480
simply because

231
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,640
a puppeteer was found at the crime scene,

232
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,800
you attribute the puppets

233
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,480
to the puppeteer based on speculation.

234
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:17,200
Lord Zhang, relying on your own guesses and imagination

235
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:19,880
to convict a woman from the Western Regions,

236
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:22,680
really makes one suspect you of regional discrimination.

237
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,760
How dare you, Lu Shijie!

238
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:24,920
Do not fabricate accusations

239
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:25,640
and use underhanded tactics.

240
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:26,480
I wouldn't dare.

241
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,320
If Your Lordship wants to convict Yuan Ran,

242
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,760
you can issue a reward notice

243
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,320
to find witnesses among the commoners from last night.

244
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,680
Engaging in a war of words with me in this court now

245
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:35,240
before the Great Ming laws

246
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,760
is meaningless.

247
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,440
Zhang Yi,

248
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:43,680
how could you handle this case so carelessly?

249
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,200
This matter was my oversight.

250
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:49,640
Focusing all my energy on

251
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,080
the pursuit of Li Chenyang

252
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,320
meant the Grand Court of Justice could only achieve this much.

253
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,720
My Lord,

254
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,440
blame me for the lack of evidence.

255
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,440
But Tang Xi hijacking Li Chenyang

256
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,840
was tracked personally by me,

257
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,920
and I exchanged blows with her.

258
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,320
The martial arts and hidden weapons she used

259
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,240
were all from the Tang Clan.

260
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,160
Lord Zhang,

261
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,520
the Great Ming Penal Code clearly states

262
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:11,240
the principles of pursuit, sentencing, and classification.

263
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,120
I know that.

264
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,200
The Great Ming Code's regulations on arrests state

265
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,400
that arresting a suspect requires a squad of more than one,

266
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,360
acting together to make the arrest,

267
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:19,000
to avoid false accusations

268
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:20,480
or misjudgments.

269
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:22,360
What?

270
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:23,440
Are you trying to teach me my job?

271
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,560
I wouldn't dare.

272
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,440
I am just kindly reminding you, My Lord,

273
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:28,600
so that in this year's Censorate-hosted

274
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,760
Great Ming Law examination,

275
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,640
you do not miss the easy points.

276
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:32,240
You...

277
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:33,920
There is something you all may not know.

278
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:35,240
The Tang Clan Young Master, Tang Xi,

