aside from the binding of mutual interests,

564
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:24,920
there remains only

565
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,880
the trust that you won't

566
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,040
kill us to silence us

567
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,560
The Young Master of the Tang Clan

568
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:35,040
sees things clearly indeed

569
00:26:35,600 --> 00:26:37,720
I like working with smart people

570
00:26:38,360 --> 00:26:39,960
Help me get one step closer to

571
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,360
Eunuch Lord Shang Hua of the Eastern Depot,

572
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,880
so I can find out the latest news

573
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:47,080
If the Eastern Depot's true secret intelligence site

574
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,680
was so easy to find,

575
00:26:50,120 --> 00:26:50,880
it wouldn't require you

576
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:52,640
to worry so much about it

577
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:56,480
Simple

578
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:59,400
The old fool has been ill recently

579
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:02,480
It's time to pay him a visit

580
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:09,600
Is Lord Shen injured?

581
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:11,720
Should we go to the Grand Court of Justice to treat it first?

582
00:27:12,600 --> 00:27:13,520
You don't need to worry about my business

583
00:27:13,800 --> 00:27:15,000
You should worry about yourself first

584
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:15,720
Lord Zhang,

585
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:18,920
leave Commander Shen to us to arrange

586
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:21,000
You should go back and rest early

587
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,160
It seems this Lord Shen

588
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,880
is quite a formidable character

589
00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:57,360
Lin Feng

590
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:00,520
I will kill you

591
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:01,600
Lin Feng

592
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:04,040
You shameless eunuch thief

593
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,800
You destroyed our lives

594
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:08,160
The hatred of taking my wife, Shuoyue

595
00:28:08,360 --> 00:28:09,640
Is absolutely irreconcilable

596
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:12,040
Lin Feng

597
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,600
You had a nightmare

598
00:28:23,040 --> 00:28:25,280
Hearing about this Zhang Yi character last night

599
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:29,000
Reminded me of unpleasant past events

600
00:28:29,320 --> 00:28:31,240
You need not explain to me

601
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:33,280
You are beneath only one

602
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,400
And above ten thousand, Eunuch Lord

603
00:28:36,920 --> 00:28:38,320
Even if you took my life

604
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:40,800
Who would dare say a word?

605
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:43,440
You have a sharp tongue

606
00:28:45,480 --> 00:28:46,040
Attendants

607
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:49,360
Here

608
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:50,760
Go to the Eastern Depot

609
00:28:51,280 --> 00:28:52,920
Notify Grand Judge Pei Yuandong

610
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,480
And Vice Minister of the Dali Temple Zhang Yi

611
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,920
To go there and wait together

612
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:56,920
Yes

613
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:30,680
Youzhi

614
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,440
What matter

615
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,520
Nearly made you lose your composure?

616
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:37,720
Nothing escapes your eyes

617
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:40,640
Western Depot Commander Wang Zhi

618
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:43,400
Has arrived at the Eastern Depot hall to demand answers

619
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:49,920
Attendants

620
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:51,520
Change my clothes

621
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,000
Hold it tight.

622
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,280
This is Consort Wan's new favorite.

623
00:30:28,600 --> 00:30:30,200
If anything goes wrong,

624
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,760
not only will your head roll,

625
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:35,200
but perhaps the Eastern Depot's

626
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,640
Grand Secretary Eunuch position

627
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,240
will also change hands.

628
00:30:39,760 --> 00:30:41,040
Eunuch Lord Wang,

629
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:44,480
whether my Grand Secretary Eunuch position changes

630
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:46,840
is for His Majesty to decide.

631
00:30:48,040 --> 00:30:49,000
Could it be that

632
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:52,120
you can now make decisions for His Majesty?

633
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:56,760
It seems the newly appointed Commander Song

634
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:59,040
wants to test my Western Depot's capabilities.

635
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,080
Very well.

636
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:04,680
Tomorrow I will petition His Majesty

637
00:31:05,080 --> 00:31:06,640
to satisfy your request.

638
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,520
Recently, regarding how the commoners

639
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,240
are discussing the Grand Court of Justice

640
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,040
and the Eastern Depot's

641
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:18,960
handling of cases,

642
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:20,640
Master Pei,

643
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:21,920
have you heard?

644
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:24,600
I have heard a little.

645
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,560
The Grand Court arrested a suspect,

646
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,760
only to release him as innocent in the end.

647
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,640
Making the Grand Court and Eastern Depot

648
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:34,080
a laughingstock among the people.

649
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:35,600
For this matter,

650
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:37,840
someone must take responsibility,

651
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:40,040
lest others in the court

652
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,480
follow suit.

653
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,680
I am truly ashamed.

654
00:31:46,040 --> 00:31:47,800
To express my apology,

655
00:31:48,040 --> 00:31:49,440
tomorrow I will ask His Majesty

656
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:52,280
for permission to resign as Grand Judge

657
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:53,960
and return to my hometown.

658
00:31:55,240 --> 00:31:58,000
That Master Pei has such awareness

659
00:31:58,560 --> 00:32:00,960
is truly a model for the court.

660
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,120
Eunuch Lord Wang,

661
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:04,960
the fault does not lie with Master Pei.

662
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:06,680
It was my eagerness to solve the case

663
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:07,520
and acting on my own initiative

664
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:08,680
that caused the current situation

665
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:10,560
for the Grand Court and Eastern Depot.

666
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:12,800
Zhang Yi!

667
00:32:12,840 --> 00:32:14,360
I am willing to bear all responsibility.

668
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,400
Zhang Yi,

669
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,600
you're one who dares to take charge.

670
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:22,120
Since the foolish act

671
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:23,800
of arresting a suspect without evidence

672
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,480
was single-handedly orchestrated

673
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:26,320
by Vice Minister Zhang,

674
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:26,800
then...

675
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:27,800
"Laws are

676
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,240
the tools of governance,

677
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:33,600
not the source of order and chaos."

678
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:37,200
Our founding Emperor valued the rule of law

679
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:39,960
and compiled the thirty volumes of the Great Ming Code.

680
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:41,920
Which volume mentions

681
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:45,200
that ineffective work by Grand Court officials

682
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,960
leading to public criticism

683
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:48,760
is a punishable offense?

684
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:51,400
Godfather,

685
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,440
you have misunderstood.

686
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:53,800
You were ill

687
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:55,000
and recuperating.

688
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:57,320
It was these useless people

689
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:59,800
who let Feng Hai, Li Chenyang's execution supervisor, suffer.

690
00:33:00,080 --> 00:33:01,680
The criminal official Li Chenyang escaped

691
00:33:02,120 --> 00:33:03,680
and has not been heard from since.

692
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:06,560
Each and every one of these events

693
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:09,360
is a great humiliation for the Eastern Depot.

694
00:33:10,160 --> 00:33:10,840
For this matter,

695
00:33:11,720 --> 00:33:13,520
someone must take responsibility,

696
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:15,400
lest others in the court

697
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,520
follow suit.

698
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:31,760
You may all sit down.

699
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:43,520
Eunuch Lord Wang, you flatter me.

700
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:46,080
I am now old and frail.

701
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:48,880
All I have left is my age.

702
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:51,720
How am I qualified...

703
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:54,000
To still be called Godfather by you?

704
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:58,000
As for recent events...

705
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:02,480
One should not rejoice over joyless matters.

706
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:05,040
Nor anger over things unworthy of rage.

707
00:34:06,800 --> 00:34:08,040
I have seen through it all.

708
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:10,520
You need not take it to heart either.

709
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:14,120
It is you, Godfather, who has taken it to heart.

710
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:17,040
Though I am Eunuch Lord of the Western Depot...

711
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:19,360
I have never dared to forget...

712
00:34:19,720 --> 00:34:22,440
The kindness of your mentorship and promotion, Godfather.

713
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:25,040
I always wish for everything to go your way...

714
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:27,560
So you may enjoy your old age in peace.

715
00:34:30,240 --> 00:34:31,760
Treat the real as empty.

716
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:33,760
Treat the empty as real.

717
00:34:36,200 --> 00:34:38,000
You and I treat each other with sincerity.

718
00:34:38,080 --> 00:34:39,160
Yet sincerity is met with rifts.

719
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:41,120
As for...

720
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:44,880
Eunuch Lord Wang valuing my cultivation of character...

721
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:47,160
Then you should not let minor details...

722
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:48,200
Harm the greater integrity.

723
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,200
Instead of seeking profit for me...

724
00:34:51,720 --> 00:34:52,640
It would be better...

725
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,320
To seek peace.

726
00:34:57,520 --> 00:34:58,480
Right now...

727
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,160
I ask for very little.

728
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:03,680
Eunuch Lord Wang.

729
00:35:04,120 --> 00:35:07,080
Early this morning, in the name of the Western Depot...

730
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:09,200
You came to the Eastern Depot to condemn us.

731
00:35:10,520 --> 00:35:11,760
In what way...

732
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:14,680
Is this showing filial respect to your Godfather?

733
00:35:16,040 --> 00:35:16,880
Filial respect...

734
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:18,680
Is naturally not expressed in words.

735
00:35:20,560 --> 00:35:23,040
Bring up the gift I prepared for Godfather.

736
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:33,080
Godfather.

737
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:35,200
Knowing you love calligraphy and painting...

738
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:36,800
A few days ago...

739
00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:39,120
I specifically asked His Majesty for a reward.

740
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:41,800
A painting by His Majesty's own hand.

741
00:35:43,160 --> 00:35:44,280
The famous Song Dynasty Prime Minister...

742
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:46,400
Wang Anshi's "On the River".

743
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:48,200
Today...

744
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,440
I present it to you with respect.

745
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:03,200
Please, Eunuch Lord Wang...

746
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:05,000
Thank His Majesty for me.

747
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:08,840
I will certainly hang this painting carefully in my room.

748
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:15,160
Take the "Memorial on Deploying the Troops" I copied last night...

749
00:36:15,240 --> 00:36:16,480
And present it to His Majesty as a return gift.

750
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,240
In this way...

751
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,920
I imagine Godfather's mood...

752
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,760
Will surely be much smoother.

753
00:36:27,160 --> 00:36:28,200
As for you all...

754
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:32,080
If the Eastern Depot doesn't care about losing face...

755
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,920
The Western Depot will no longer pursue it either.

756
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:35,520
But remember.

757
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:37,160
Matters...

758
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:39,440
Must eventually have a conclusion.

759
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:05,280
Useless trash.

760
00:37:06,240 --> 00:37:08,120
Can't even take care of a cat properly.

761
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:11,760
How can you take care of my Godfather?

762
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:14,440
Little Xi.

763
00:37:17,720 --> 00:37:18,400
I am here.

764
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:26,560
You stay at the Eastern Depot for a day.

765
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:29,320
Teach the people serving the Eunuch Lord properly.

766
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,280
Show them...

767
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:36,200
How you take care of Consort Wan's pets.

768
00:37:37,440 --> 00:37:38,000
Yes.

769
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:43,160
Commander Wang.

770
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:45,400
His Majesty and Consort Wan are overjoyed.

771
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:47,200
They summon you to the palace immediately.

772
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:56,840
Godfather.

773
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:59,560
I will return to the palace first to serve His Majesty.

774
00:38:00,160 --> 00:38:03,440
I wish you longevity and health.

775
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:06,600
Thank you for your trouble, Lord Wang.
